{"tid":1910406,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"3月5號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-03-04T15:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T15:41:44.000Z","uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5d9f00ed2aa41dc9b303ef02f624549c65cd9816","tid":1910406,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"【#上庭聲援 - 3 月 5 日 星期四】<br />\n<br />\n►--- 10:30 am ---◄ <br />\n🏛 高 等 法 院 3 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️#杜麗冰法官<br />\n👤郭(27)🛑<strong>已還押113天</strong> 申請保釋（#1111大埔 鐵路上放置物品）"},{"pid":"a9f4a07a028c7fac2fbdda7b7e36ac78c904ad22","tid":1910406,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=dc49628c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"0d495309aacd13c2f62e99f2680025fa073fc97c","tid":1910406,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:38:42.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=20ad84c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG <br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIM5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=51d94fad\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"ed0361d970f5745ad34b54eae650daccbef11a19","tid":1910406,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SDdHknN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSDdHknN.jpg&h=b58e7b10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"243b83e0c3ebca5681333e2bd53774403d63b2f9","tid":1910406,"uid":113183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ff4cabbd8f42c533e3ca78f3bf7416c872901c9","tid":1910406,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測<br />\n</strong>- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"3b9e8dd359292b7a63ab8318110fa8159a193795","tid":1910406,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:40:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5bfc6029127cba5150a1200613d5107faff62a71","tid":1910406,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e0d5767735f524006ca40e74d201358bd2c716cb","tid":1910406,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":